@node HelpN "Develop status and Help"

 @{b}@{u}Development status and Help needed@{uu}@{ub}

  Currentlly the MassDL development is almost at a zero state.
  1st thats because I prefer coding in C++, 2nd because users interest
 for improvements is not much if any. and 3rd because the current MassDL
 fits my needs (I use it alot) and I think the main goal of it has been
 quite well reached.

@endnode

